main event: Three bright objects were observed in the sky over Washington, D.C. at 9:05 PM, which maneuvered and shot downward vertically.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 10 minutes., The objects were confirmed by USAF radar at Andrews AFB., Witnesses reported the objects possibly reflecting lights, possibly meteorological balloons., This observation occurred during a period of increased UFO sightings in the area., The weather conditions were reported to be clear sky and dry.
sighted object: three bright objects in the sky
